This is a maven project - choose maven-webapp archetype



ways to request for a page from the server
- type the url in the browser and hit enter
- hit the submit button in a html form
- <a> tags



get request
	- default 
	- here the request parameters are appended to the URL as name/value pairs
	
post request
	- have to specify explicity
	- here the request parameters are sent through the request body